00:38:18,659 --> 00:38:19,599
[SPEAKER_01] Nema,

967
00:38:19,599 --> 00:38:20,400
[SPEAKER_01] nema,

968
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:21,460
[SPEAKER_01] tu smo imali

969
00:38:21,460 --> 00:38:23,500
[SPEAKER_01] jedno neugodno iskustvo,

970
00:38:23,500 --> 00:38:23,840
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

971
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:24,400
[SPEAKER_01] bili smo,

972
00:38:25,360 --> 00:38:27,519
[SPEAKER_01] dogovorili na zadnjim izborima,

973
00:38:27,519 --> 00:38:29,920
[SPEAKER_01] koaliciju s HDZ-om na svim razinama,

974
00:38:29,920 --> 00:38:32,519
[SPEAKER_01] i onda,

975
00:38:32,519 --> 00:38:34,679
[SPEAKER_01] ovo je već za rubriku vjerovali,

976
00:38:34,679 --> 00:38:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] ili ne,

977
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:35,380
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

978
00:38:35,380 --> 00:38:37,179
[SPEAKER_01] HDZ se nije držao dogovor.

979
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:39,099
[SPEAKER_01] i onda,

980
00:38:39,099 --> 00:38:43,260
[SPEAKER_01] kako smo dogovorili pozicije na listama,

981
00:38:43,260 --> 00:38:43,619
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

982
00:38:43,619 --> 00:38:45,559
[SPEAKER_01] koje bi pripadale HSS-u,

983
00:38:45,559 --> 00:38:46,940
[SPEAKER_01] koje je HDZ-o,

984
00:38:46,940 --> 00:38:48,599
[SPEAKER_01] onda su oni to htjeli mijenjati,

985
00:38:48,599 --> 00:38:50,760
[SPEAKER_01] onda smo mi ju radili jedino,

986
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] s naše strane,

987
00:38:52,000 --> 00:38:53,219
[SPEAKER_01] što je bilo normalno,

988
00:38:53,219 --> 00:38:56,679
[SPEAKER_01] nismo se jednostavno željeli plamirati,

989
00:38:56,679 --> 00:38:58,739
[SPEAKER_01] nismo se željeli spuštati na tu razinu,

990
00:38:58,739 --> 00:39:01,519
[SPEAKER_01] koalicija već bila potpisana,

991
00:39:01,519 --> 00:39:01,880
[SPEAKER_01] ništa,

992
00:39:01,880 --> 00:39:02,820
[SPEAKER_01] nek to stoji,

993
00:39:02,820 --> 00:39:04,619
[SPEAKER_01] ko mala djeca,

994
00:39:04,619 --> 00:39:06,260
[SPEAKER_01] mi se nećemo igrati sastaviti,

995
00:39:06,260 --> 00:39:07,199
[SPEAKER_01] kako znate,

996
00:39:07,199 --> 00:39:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] i tako da u ovom sazivu

997
00:39:08,960 --> 00:39:11,139
[SPEAKER_01] ne imamo nikoga u županijskoj skupštini,

998
00:39:11,139 --> 00:39:12,300
[SPEAKER_01] ali evo, bože moj,

999
00:39:12,300 --> 00:39:13,320
[SPEAKER_01] dogodne su izbori,

1000
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:15,219
[SPEAKER_01] pa prvijen će se i to da će bović.

1001
00:39:15,219 --> 00:39:16,340
[SPEAKER_00] Nije, pa dogodne su izbori,

1002
00:39:16,340 --> 00:39:17,739
[SPEAKER_00] to se baš brzo bliže,

1003
00:39:17,739 --> 00:39:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] vidim,

1004
00:39:18,079 --> 00:39:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] recimo,

1005
00:39:18,619 --> 00:39:20,920
[SPEAKER_00] i kod Srba i kod Bošnjaka,

1006
00:39:20,920 --> 00:39:22,679
[SPEAKER_00] je predzborna kampanja već počela.

1007
00:39:22,679 --> 00:39:23,860
[SPEAKER_00] I kod HDZ?

1008
00:39:23,860 --> 00:39:24,559
[SPEAKER_01] Zar je?

1009
00:39:24,559 --> 00:39:26,019
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kako nije,

1010
00:39:26,019 --> 00:39:28,260
[SPEAKER_01] pa evo pričava sa izbornim zakonom.

1011
00:39:28,260 --> 00:39:29,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kako nije priča,

1012
00:39:29,960 --> 00:39:34,019
[SPEAKER_01] ako imate potpisan sporazum s partnerima,

1013
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:36,820
[SPEAKER_01] u ovom slučaju to trojka i Rama,

1014
00:39:36,820 --> 00:39:39,099
[SPEAKER_01] Isak i Elzina Pirići,

1015
00:39:39,099 --> 00:39:39,820
[SPEAKER_01] koji je tu još,

1016
00:39:39,820 --> 00:39:42,380
[SPEAKER_01] Sandi i Salkić imaju puno tih partnera,

1017
00:39:42,380 --> 00:39:46,699
[SPEAKER_01] opet ima to malo seksualni konotacij,

1018
00:39:46,699 --> 00:39:48,019
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

1019
00:39:48,019 --> 00:39:49,559
[SPEAKER_01] ako imate dogovor s njima,

1020
00:39:49,559 --> 00:39:50,739
[SPEAKER_01] da ste nakon u roku,

1021
00:39:50,739 --> 00:39:52,699
[SPEAKER_01] pola godine izmijeniti izborni zakon,

1022
00:39:52,699 --> 00:39:54,800
[SPEAKER_01] zašto niste kao uputili proceduru,

1023
00:39:54,800 --> 00:39:55,699
[SPEAKER_01] nakon pola godine,

1024
00:39:55,699 --> 00:39:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] zašto nakon dvi i po tri godine.

1025
00:39:58,000 --> 00:39:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je pitanje za njih?

1026
00:39:59,000 --> 00:39:59,360
[SPEAKER_00] Tako.

1027
00:39:59,360 --> 00:40:01,039
[SPEAKER_01] To je za njih pitanje.

1028
00:40:01,039 --> 00:40:01,820
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste li ih pital,

1029
00:40:01,820 --> 00:40:02,900
[SPEAKER_00] tojkada sam vam govorili?

1030
00:40:02,900 --> 00:40:03,679
[SPEAKER_01] Jesam,

1031
00:40:03,679 --> 00:40:05,019
[SPEAKER_01] pital sam ja svašta.

1032
00:40:05,019 --> 00:40:06,960
[SPEAKER_01] Možda je bolje,

1033
00:40:06,960 --> 00:40:08,380
[SPEAKER_01] evo i za moje mentalno zdrav,

1034
00:40:08,380 --> 00:40:09,380
[SPEAKER_01] i za njihovo dane,

1035
00:40:09,500 --> 00:40:13,099
[SPEAKER_01] sudjelo je sad u radu Hrvatskog narodnog sabora,

1036
00:40:13,099 --> 00:40:15,360
[SPEAKER_01] jer ima običeva postaviti svakova pitanja,

1037
00:40:15,360 --> 00:40:17,119
[SPEAKER_01] svaki vrag me zanima,

1038
00:40:17,119 --> 00:40:19,920
[SPEAKER_01] i moje misljenje nije konačno nikad,

1039
00:40:19,920 --> 00:40:21,500
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam voljam promijeniti misljenje,

1040
00:40:21,500 --> 00:40:25,900
[SPEAKER_01] ali uz ozbiljnu argumentaciju da mi neko obrazloši.

1041
00:40:25,900 --> 00:40:29,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ali većinovna ta pitanja koja ja postavim,

1042
00:40:29,159 --> 00:40:31,059
[SPEAKER_01] ostane samo mug s druge strane,

1043
00:40:31,059 --> 00:40:33,659
[SPEAKER_01] neće ni da pokušaju odgovoriti,

1044
00:40:33,659 --> 00:40:35,559
[SPEAKER_01] onda nešto nije u redu.

1045
00:40:35,559 --> 00:40:39,199
[SPEAKER_01] Onda kad već i nakon te dvi i po tri godine

1046
