[SPEAKER_01] uputiti taj zakon u proceduru,

1047
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:44,400
[SPEAKER_01] zbog čega onda napuštanje sjednice,

1048
00:40:44,400 --> 00:40:46,539
[SPEAKER_01] u trenutku kad se treba glasati o njemu.

1049
00:40:46,539 --> 00:40:50,239
[SPEAKER_01] Šta se onda to kaže?

1050
00:40:50,239 --> 00:40:51,599
[SPEAKER_01] Prekin će on sjednicu,

1051
00:40:51,599 --> 00:40:52,719
[SPEAKER_01] kaže glasati se sad.

1052
00:40:52,719 --> 00:40:55,400
[SPEAKER_01] Alo, pa poslali zakon u proceduru

1053
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:56,340
[SPEAKER_01] da se o njemu glasa.

1054
00:40:56,340 --> 00:40:59,320
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kaže, možda ne bi prošao.

1055
00:40:59,320 --> 00:41:00,719
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo, kako znaš.

1056
00:41:00,719 --> 00:41:03,019
[SPEAKER_01] Drugo, pa ako ne bi prošao,

1057
00:41:03,019 --> 00:41:04,300
[SPEAKER_01] pa znaćeš ko je protiv.

1058
00:41:04,300 --> 00:41:06,940
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ćeš mu se revanširat,

1059
00:41:06,940 --> 00:41:08,900
[SPEAKER_01] da možda nećeš imenovat,

1060
00:41:08,900 --> 00:41:10,320
[SPEAKER_01] Bakira Hađe Omerovića

1061
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:12,099
[SPEAKER_01] za ravnatelja federalne televizije.

1062
00:41:12,099 --> 00:41:14,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, nisu to odlučili.

1063
00:41:14,699 --> 00:41:16,099
[SPEAKER_01] Odlučili s pobići,

1064
00:41:16,099 --> 00:41:17,780
[SPEAKER_01] znači, da ne glasaju o zakonu

1065
00:41:17,780 --> 00:41:19,820
[SPEAKER_01] koji su oni uputili u proceduru.

1066
00:41:19,820 --> 00:41:22,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ova Herceg-Bosanska četvorka,

1067
00:41:22,099 --> 00:41:24,260
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo nešto razgovarao,

1068
00:41:24,260 --> 00:41:25,099
[SPEAKER_01] razmišljali,

1069
00:41:25,099 --> 00:41:28,400
[SPEAKER_01] postoje četiri varijante

1070
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:30,199
[SPEAKER_01] izbornog zakona

1071
00:41:30,199 --> 00:41:32,320
[SPEAKER_01] koje je Hrvatski Narodni Sabor

1072
