[SPEAKER_01] pripremio,

1073
00:41:33,139 --> 00:41:34,840
[SPEAKER_01] ova je predlog Marine Pendeš

1074
00:41:34,840 --> 00:41:36,159
[SPEAKER_01] i jedna od tih varijanta.

1075
00:41:36,340 --> 00:41:39,380
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo uradili još jednu varijantu

1076
00:41:39,380 --> 00:41:40,639
[SPEAKER_01] i ovo,

1077
00:41:40,639 --> 00:41:42,820
[SPEAKER_01] ako se brzo ne raspetlja,

1078
00:41:42,820 --> 00:41:44,260
[SPEAKER_01] teško da će se raspetljati,

1079
00:41:44,260 --> 00:41:45,239
[SPEAKER_01] evo i ova sjednica

1080
00:41:45,239 --> 00:41:46,280
[SPEAKER_01] koja vam trebala biti,

1081
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:47,360
[SPEAKER_01] neće biti održana,

1082
00:41:47,360 --> 00:41:48,840
[SPEAKER_01] vjerovatno,

1083
00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:51,300
[SPEAKER_01] mi ćemo uput svoj predlog zakona.

1084
00:41:52,179 --> 00:41:53,179
[SPEAKER_01] gospodin Svitanović

1085
00:41:53,179 --> 00:41:54,739
[SPEAKER_01] je to u ime ove četiri stranke

1086
00:41:54,739 --> 00:41:56,639
[SPEAKER_01] uput i sigurno ćemo

1087
00:41:56,639 --> 00:41:58,019
[SPEAKER_01] barem ostati na glasanju.

1088
00:41:58,019 --> 00:41:59,480
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da vidimo ko će...

1089
00:41:59,480 --> 00:42:00,639
[SPEAKER_00] Kako izgleda je predlog?

1090
00:42:00,639 --> 00:42:01,760
[SPEAKER_00] Po čemu se razlikuje?

1091
00:42:01,760 --> 00:42:02,579
[SPEAKER_00] Prekrasno,

1092
00:42:02,579 --> 00:42:03,760
[SPEAKER_00] kako kaže Donald Trump.

1093
00:42:03,760 --> 00:42:05,639
[SPEAKER_01] Pa u principu

1094
00:42:05,639 --> 00:42:07,480
[SPEAKER_01] zasniva se na elektorskim glasovima.

1095
00:42:07,480 --> 00:42:09,519
[SPEAKER_01] Zasniva se na elektorskim glasovima.

1096
00:42:09,519 --> 00:42:10,980
[SPEAKER_01] Zasniva se na to,

1097
00:42:10,980 --> 00:42:11,300
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

1098
00:42:11,300 --> 00:42:13,019
[SPEAKER_01] da bi HRŽ, ZHŽ,

1099
00:42:13,019 --> 00:42:15,980
[SPEAKER_01] da bi davali veći broj elektora Hrvata,

1100
00:42:15,980 --> 00:42:17,360
[SPEAKER_01] a davali bi, recimo,

1101
