1106
00:42:26,659 --> 00:42:28,440
[SPEAKER_01] tako da se ne bi moglo dogoditi.

1107
00:42:28,440 --> 00:42:30,360
[SPEAKER_00] I onda rješava i sljedić Finci

1108
00:42:30,360 --> 00:42:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] i sve strane.

1109
00:42:31,119 --> 00:42:32,480
[SPEAKER_00] Rješava apsolutno sve.

1110
00:42:32,480 --> 00:42:33,099
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1111
00:42:33,099 --> 00:42:35,340
[SPEAKER_01] sve se to spodi na to

1112
00:42:35,340 --> 00:42:37,639
[SPEAKER_01] da se samo traže razloz

1113
00:42:37,639 --> 00:42:38,760
[SPEAKER_01] zašto da se nešto

1114
00:42:38,760 --> 00:42:40,820
[SPEAKER_01] ne implementira.

1115
00:42:40,820 --> 00:42:44,420
[SPEAKER_01] Stranke, sve iz Republike Srpske

1116
00:42:44,420 --> 00:42:44,940
[SPEAKER_01] su rekli,

1117
00:42:44,940 --> 00:42:46,139
[SPEAKER_01] nama sve odgovara,

1118
00:42:46,139 --> 00:42:48,860
[SPEAKER_01] mi ostavljamo direktan izbor.

1119
00:42:48,860 --> 00:42:50,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ako hoćete,

1120
00:42:50,340 --> 00:42:52,059
[SPEAKER_01] mi ćemo samo promijeniti,

1121
00:42:52,059 --> 00:42:53,320
[SPEAKER_01] nek se promijeni ustav,

1122
00:42:53,320 --> 00:42:55,139
[SPEAKER_01] Republika Srpska bira jednog.

1123
00:42:55,139 --> 00:42:57,280
[SPEAKER_01] Po evo, koga godi zabere,

1124
00:42:57,280 --> 00:43:00,820
[SPEAKER_01] sad i tu je jednostavan izlaz.

1125
00:43:00,820 --> 00:43:01,119
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1126
00:43:01,119 --> 00:43:02,719
[SPEAKER_01] Herceg-Bosna bira jednog,

1127
00:43:02,719 --> 00:43:04,519
[SPEAKER_01] Saraj-Bosna bira jednog,

1128
00:43:04,519 --> 00:43:05,840
[SPEAKER_01] svi se mogu kandidirati.

1129
00:43:05,840 --> 00:43:07,800
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nek narod odluči,

1130
00:43:07,800 --> 00:43:08,059
[SPEAKER_01] mislim,

1131
00:43:08,059 --> 00:43:08,820
[SPEAKER_01] čemu je problem.

1132
00:43:09,059 --> 00:43:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] nešto slično je pisao i ovaj

1133
00:43:10,980 --> 00:43:12,280
