1135
00:43:14,860 --> 00:43:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Amerikanac je korijena iz Čitluka,

1136
00:43:18,000 --> 00:43:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] koliko vidim,

1137
00:43:18,619 --> 00:43:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] i blizaki je Trumpovoj administraciji.

1138
00:43:21,340 --> 00:43:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, on je baš objavio jedan nesaj

1139
00:43:23,059 --> 00:43:24,900
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem poziva

1140
00:43:24,900 --> 00:43:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] na ukidanje OHR-a,

1141
00:43:26,960 --> 00:43:28,900
[SPEAKER_00] formiranje tri federalne jedinice.

1142
00:43:28,900 --> 00:43:30,719
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ovo sa neke njegove,

1143
00:43:30,719 --> 00:43:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] ukratko, preporuke sam stavio na papir.

1144
00:43:33,039 --> 00:43:35,179
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, ukidanje OHR-a i bonskih oblasti.

1145
00:43:35,260 --> 00:43:38,960
[SPEAKER_00] Uspostava tri federalne jedinice

1146
00:43:38,960 --> 00:43:40,340
[SPEAKER_00] bez razmene teritorija,

1147
00:43:40,340 --> 00:43:42,780
[SPEAKER_00] obnova prava Hrvatskog naroda

1148
00:43:42,780 --> 00:43:44,880
[SPEAKER_00] na izbor legitimnih predstavnika,

1149
00:43:44,880 --> 00:43:47,780
[SPEAKER_00] smanjenje utjecaja state departmenta

1150
00:43:47,780 --> 00:43:49,099
[SPEAKER_00] i zamjena karijernih

1151
00:43:49,099 --> 00:43:50,940
[SPEAKER_00] političkim diplomatima u regiji.

1152
00:43:50,940 --> 00:43:53,940
[SPEAKER_00] Mi sad, nemo nikakvog veliposlanika američkog.

1153
00:43:53,940 --> 00:43:55,840
[SPEAKER_01] Nemamo, ali inače,

1154
00:43:55,840 --> 00:43:56,420
[SPEAKER_01] pravilo,

1155
00:43:56,420 --> 00:43:59,340
[SPEAKER_01] politički diplomat američki

1156
00:43:59,340 --> 00:44:00,559
[SPEAKER_01] ide u Zagreba,

1157
00:44:00,559 --> 00:44:02,719
[SPEAKER_01] Beograd i Sarajevo

1158
00:44:02,719 --> 00:44:04,500
[SPEAKER_01] dobijaju karijerne diplomate,

1159
00:44:04,500 --> 00:44:05,719
[SPEAKER_01] znači, tu su oni

1160
00:44:05,719 --> 00:44:08,139
[SPEAKER_01] nešto ko Jandroković

1161
00:44:08,139 --> 00:44:09,559
[SPEAKER_01] u HDZ-u, koji valjaju

1162
00:44:09,559 --> 00:44:10,940
[SPEAKER_01] svakoj administraciji

1163
00:44:10,940 --> 00:44:12,199
[SPEAKER_01] i koji su tu samo, eto,

1164
00:44:12,199 --> 00:44:13,860
[SPEAKER_01] da prođe vrijeme

1165
00:44:13,860 --> 00:44:16,460
[SPEAKER_01] i tako da bi to imalo logike,

1166
00:44:16,460 --> 00:44:18,460
[SPEAKER_01] iako ja mislim da Bosna i Hercegovina

1167
00:44:18,460 --> 00:44:19,739
[SPEAKER_01] nije u fokusu

1168
00:44:19,739 --> 00:44:22,000
